<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Contacto | SousaDigitalLab</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            background: #f1f3f6;
        }

        /* HEADER / NAVBAR */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c, #2575fc);
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .navbar {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .navbar a {
            color: #ffffffcc;
            margin: 0 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .navbar a:hover,
        .navbar a.active {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        /* CONTENT */
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.08);
        }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #1a2a6c;
        }

        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            margin-top: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        button {
            background: #2575fc;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: #1a2a6c;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header class="header">
    <div class="logo">SousaDigitalLab</div>
    <nav class="navbar">
        index.htmlInício</a>
        servicos.htmlServiços</a>
        contacto.htmlContactos</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Entrar em Contacto</h2>
        <p>Utilize o formulário abaixo ou contacte diretamente por email.</p>

        <form>
            <label>Nome</label>
            <input type="text" placeholder="O seu nome">

            <label>Email</label>
            <input type="email" placeholder="O seu email">

            <label>Mensagem</label>
            <textarea rows="6" placeholder="Escreva a sua mensagem aqui"></textarea>

            <button type="submit">Enviar</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Contacto Direto</h2>
        sousadigitallab@gmail.com
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
